Necross/ Splattercannon:

Necross bows and turns to leave.  Splattercannon followed, and shortly arrived in Malic's holding area.  Malice was sitting up, unable to move.  Hellplague stood behind the bounty hunter readying her equipment.
"Unicron sent us to help you."  Necross said bluntly, Splattercannon remained silent.
